---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Anna Vidal   ";
---
<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="gif">
        <img width="300" height="259" alt="RaccoonSpaceGif" src="/space.webp"/>
    </div>
    <!-- <h1>Anna</h1> -->
    <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
        <span class="badge">Software tester & product owner</span>
    </div>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
        Hi! I'm Anna and I have +5 years of experience in software development.
        <br><br> 
        Being quality-focused led me to pursue more product and testing-oriented roles, 
        where I can leverage my technical development experience to ensure software solutions are not only functional but also meet user requirements. 
        Testing allows me to stay technical while being inolved in user and business needs :) 
        <br><br>
        Certifications:<br>
        - Product Owner (Scrum, Six Sigma)<br>
        - Software Tester (ISTQB).
    </p>
    <!-- <div class="center">
        <a href="/projects/">
            <button class="btn">My portfolio</button>
        </a>
    </div> -->
    <!-- <h2>Skills</h2> -->
    <div class="skills center">
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Python" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/python/python-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="CSS" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/css3/css3-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="HTML" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/html5/html5-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="JavaScript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Git" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/git/git-original.svg"/>
    </div>
    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <p>
        Outside of tech, my main interest is the environment. 
        After finishing my studies in Natural Sciences, I worked as a nature guide in the High Arctic, in Svalbard. 
        Currently I'm a second-year student of BA Philosophy, Politics and Economics with an interest in environmental policy, ecological economics and conservation.
        In my free time you will find me gardening and growing my own food, sewing, and cooking.
    </p>
</Layout>

